title: Muddy Creek (Nodaway River tributary)
text:
Muddy Creek is a <a href="stream">stream</a> in <a href="Nodaway%20County%2C%20Missouri">Nodaway County</a> in the <a href="U.S.%20state">U.S. state</a> of <a href="Missouri">Missouri</a>. It is a tributary of <a href="Nodaway%20River">Nodaway River</a>.
Muddy Creek was so named on account of its usually muddy water.
